Package org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.coord.subprocess

Interface Summary
IAeSpCoordinating Interface indicating a AE subprocess protocol type coordinating activity.
IAeSpCoordinator Interface for AE Subprocess coordination type coordinator.
IAeSpParticipant Interface for AE Subprocess coordination type participant.
IAeSpProtocolMessage Interface for AE Subprocess coordination type protcol messages.
 

Class Summary
AeProcessTerminateWork Wraps the process termination code in a Work impl so that it can be run asynchronously.
AeSpCoordinatingBase Base class for subprocess type coordinated activities.
AeSpCoordinationMessages Coordination messages used in the AE subprocess Participant Completion coordination protocol.
AeSpCoordinationStates AE subprocess protocol coordination states loosely based on Business Agreement protocol described in the BPEL-4WS 1.1, appendix C.
AeSpCoordinator Implementation of a AE subprocess protcol coordinator.
AeSpParticipant Implementation of a participant, based on the AE subprocess coordination protocol.
AeSpProtocolMessage  
AeSpProtocolTable Defines a AE Subprocess protocol state table.
